Package: FAIRR
Title: Functional Approximation of Impulse Responses
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Gauthier", "Serres", email = "gauthierserres@outlook.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the Functional Approximation of Impulse Responses (FAIR) methodology. This package allows for the estimation of symmetric and asymmetric impulse response functions by approximating them as a linear combination of Gaussian basis or exponential basis functions using Stan.
